reviewText: This dvd is actually just the previous Manson documentary "Fear of a Satanic Planet" with a new cover. its entirely the same dvd, just a different name and cover. it has all the same stuff as the other dvd, even the same exact menu. the documentary itself is so-so. none of the music on it is Marilyn Manson.
This is an unauthorized biography of Marilyn Manson's history through rare archival footage and interviews with friends, colleagues, and critics.  Not a music video DVD...
